Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.72,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Roxanne came with an outfit.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.84,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll include one with her, \Nthen I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.18,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.65,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,It costs 4,000 nars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.72,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:03.81,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, since I owe you \Nfor assisting me the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:08.73,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,how about 177,800 nars for both?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.89,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.57,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.31,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I have this 30% discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.71,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to have a nice chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.15,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.59,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,About the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.27,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to have her come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.48,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.24,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Did I imagine that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.78,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like her face \Nclouded over for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:54.34,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Did it seem that way because I feel guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.74,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,or because I want her to be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.97,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.30,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry, approach the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.65,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.16,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.34,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for joining the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.60,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's a ton of hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.22,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.97,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Roxanne, the number one slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.01,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.97,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,When was the "number one slave" \Nposition established?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.97,Main - Top,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,So you are a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.35,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.94,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,His wife? Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.71,Main - Top,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you once stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:32.15,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Roxanne, I wish you hadn't \Ndenied that so flatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.15,Main - Top,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,You have such nice clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.49,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,and your hair is such a pretty color.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.41,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,It's because my master is a \Nkind and wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:43.37,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing to worry about when it \Ncomes to clothes, food, and housing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.09,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,The contract is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.11,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Please check your Intelligence Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.90,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.80,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.68,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\c&H000000&\3c&H978A2A&\bord2\alpha&H60&\b1\fscx80\blur2\fs6\pos(396,68)}Sherry <Female 16 Years Old> Explorer – Slave\N{\fscx90}Owner: Kaga Michio
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.47,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Here's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.35,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\c&H000000&\3c&HB7C349&\fs4\bord2\alpha&H60&\fscx91\blur2\b1\pos(436,51)}Kaga Michio <Male 17 Years Old> Explorer – Free Man\N{\fscx100}Owned Slaves: Roxanne, Sherry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.89,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.98,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.80,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,The clothes will take some time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.60,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,Please return in ten days' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:15.85,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:19.74,Main,ALAN,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.12,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.99,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Party Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:29.67,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\pos(128,82)\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20}[Party]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:29.67,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20\pos(70,122)\an4}Kaga Michio
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:29.67,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20\an4\pos(70,164)}Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.47,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.50,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll join.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.67,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20\an4\pos(70,203)}Sherry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.67,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:33.04,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're a member of our party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.17,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:37.24,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,And now I can finally check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.93,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Party Job Settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.43,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\pos(128,82)\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20}[Party]
