Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.43,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20\an4\pos(70,164)}Roxanne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.43,Onscreen_Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs10\c&HFFFFFF&\fsp2\1a&H20\an4\pos(70,203)}Sherry
