Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.05,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\fscy140\an8\b1\1a&H40&\pos(276,165)}1st Explorer Lv 10
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.05,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\fscy140\an8\b1\1a&H20&\pos(445,85)}Jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.05,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\fscy140\an8\b1\1a&H40&\pos(446,240)}Explorer: Lv 10\N Villager Lv 3\N Herbalist: Lv 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.05,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Blacksmith really isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.80,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't know the conditions for \Nunlocking it, there's not much I can say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.18,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.06,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to have Sherry \Ntry a bunch of different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:54.83,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we head back to our house in Quratar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.21,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.07,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.45,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Ms. Roxanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.13,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:08.16,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are there Adventurers in this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.33,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.75,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,He just said we'd be going back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:17.46,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she thinks we're going to use Field Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.34,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Since I showed her my Intelligence Card,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.39,Status Text,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0\c&H000000&\3c&HB7C349&\fs4\bord2\alpha&H60&\fscx91\blur2\b1\pos(436,51)}Kaga Michio <Male 17 Years Old> Explorer – Free Man\N{\fscx100}Owned Slaves: Roxanne, Sherry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.39,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,she knows I'm an Explorer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.60,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,and Field Walk is an Adventurer skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.81,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It does seem odd that I can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.12,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not sure how to explain it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.50,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Come with us, and you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.65,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't even try to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:40.80,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been convenient if she'd \Noffered some kind of explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:42.63,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.28,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.37,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.87,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.25,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.17,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:00.75,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. She's confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.01,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.15,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,You can sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.06,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.68,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. We'll even be eating together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.06,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What? We'll be eating together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.62,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,He's our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:23.66,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home in Quratar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:26.13,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, you'll be living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.74,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.63,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:34.29,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Are you capable of using multiple jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.99,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she figured that out without any hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:41.01,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Close. I don't have the Adventurer job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:44.16,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,What we used earlier was a \Ntransportation spell called Teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.48,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:48.97,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry, do you know people \Nwith multiple jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:52.35,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Myths mention gods like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:56.35,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Then think of me as that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.71,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,But myths are made up stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.61,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.33,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.67,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weapon would you \Nlike to use in the labyrinths?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.62,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good with a spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.33,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'll be fighting alongside \Nallies on the front lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.25,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,then a maul would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.50,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,A maul?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.99,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:19.64,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, defeating monsters \Nwith a sword and defeating monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:22.67,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,with bare hands were the conditions \Nfor becoming a swordsman and a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:26.61,Italics,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,A hammer would suit a Blacksmith, so maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.93,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry, have you ever beaten \Na monster with a maul?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.33,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.92,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Then try using a maul for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.71,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that, Roxanne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.45,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:39.84,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep monsters in check \Nby serving as the front line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:43.60,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,so you can prepare to cast \Nspells from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.64,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What? Spells? \NYou mean like offensive spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:47.23,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:48.95,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.45,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,I can use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:51.95,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,He can use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.30,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.96,Main,MICHIO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.23,Main,ROXANNE,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.07,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.97,Main,SHERRY,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood.
